import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.sin(x1)
    v1 = jnp.minimum(v0, v0)
    v2 = jnp.cos(x0)
    v3 = jnp.abs(x1)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(v3, v0)
    v5 = jnp.add(v1, v3)
